public class FigureAttributeConstant
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

A FigureAttribute is a constant for accessing a special figure attribute. It does not contain a value but just defines a unique attribute ID. Therefore, they provide a type-safe way of defining attribute constants. (SourceForge feature request ID: <>)
